article_title: Look how Obama’s helped the health care industry [pic] – twitchy.com
article_text:
On its own, that tweet probably doesn’t seem all that special. But when you put it next to another one, the result is pure magic:

This could not be more perfect. pic.twitter.com/Hsv0LIxQHz — Countermoonbat (@CounterMoonbat) February 25, 2016

Kinda says it all, no?
